               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. KYDD</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> "What is the size of the room? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About ten feet by eight—half of it was taken up to form an office board—I wanted them to go altogether, and in consideration of their moving out of the house, I allowed them to retain the back room as an office.</p>
