                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Had you ever any notice of any meeting of the society, or did you attend any? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18631026-name-531" type="witnessName">
